body:
@zachbateman You can reproduce this with the drag_and_drop example or only your own code? I'm not able to reproduce with the example. 

> That combined with the overall intermittent behavior has me wondering if this may be due to a system/update ordering issue/ambiguity?

That seems plausible, but I thought that bevy now printed warnings when system order was ambiguous unless you opted in to it (e.g. https://docs.rs/bevy/latest/bevy/prelude/trait.IntoScheduleConfigs.html#method.ambiguous_with)
